### Variables
@hostname = localhost
@port = 3000
@baseUrl = http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}

### 1. Test the Home Route
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Check Engine Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/status
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Create a New Compliance Log
POST {{baseUrl}}/logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "action": "Initial Regulatory Audit - Chicago Property",
